fde_problem_matrix:
  - problem_type: Intake_and_Convergence
    description: >
      Turning vague, conflicting, or incomplete stakeholder input into a
      shared, explicit understanding of what is actually being built.
    common_signals:
      - "We need AI here"
      - Conflicting stakeholder goals
      - No single source of truth
      - Moving requirements
    typical_artifacts:
      - Convergence brief
      - Scope boundaries
      - Success criteria
      - One-way vs two-way decision classification
    palette_solution:
      - Enforce convergence before execution
      - Semantic blueprint creation
      - Decision logging (why, not just what)
    industries:
      - Logistics
      - Enterprise SaaS
      - Fintech
      - Healthcare
      - Government

  - problem_type: Human_to_System_Translation
    description: >
      Converting tribal knowledge, business rules, and human judgment
      into deterministic or probabilistic system logic.
    common_signals:
      - Rules live in people's heads
      - "It depends" logic
      - Exception-heavy workflows
    typical_artifacts:
      - Rule catalogs
      - Decision trees
      - Prompt templates
      - Policy-to-code mappings
    palette_solution:
      - RIU-based rule extraction
      - Explicit ambiguity capture
      - Reversible decision tagging
    industries:
      - Logistics
      - Compliance
      - Ads
      - Customer support
      - Operations

  - problem_type: Systems_Integration
    description: >
      Making poorly documented, inconsistent, or legacy systems
      interoperate reliably in production.
    common_signals:
      - Undocumented APIs
      - Brittle integrations
      - Manual glue code
    typical_artifacts:
      - Integration contracts
      - Data schemas
      - Failure-handling paths
    palette_solution:
      - Reverse-engineering playbooks
      - Explicit interface contracts
      - Integration RIUs
    industries:
      - Logistics
      - Payments
      - Enterprise IT
      - Supply chain

  - problem_type: Data_Semantics_and_Quality
    description: >
      Ensuring that data means what people think it means, and that models
      are trained, evaluated, and operated on reliable inputs.
    common_signals:
      - Inconsistent labels
      - Silent data drift
      - Model performance degradation
    typical_artifacts:
      - Data dictionaries
      - Evaluation harnesses
      - Quality thresholds
    palette_solution:
      - Semantic validation RIUs
      - Continuous evaluation loops
      - Agent maturity tracking
    industries:
      - AI/ML
      - Analytics
      - Search
      - Recommendations

  - problem_type: Reliability_and_Failure_Handling
    description: >
      Managing systems that work most of the time, but fail in
      non-obvious, high-impact ways.
    common_signals:
      - Works in staging, fails in prod
      - Long MTTR
      - No clear owner during incidents
    typical_artifacts:
      - Runbooks
      - Escalation paths
      - Failure taxonomies
    palette_solution:
      - Failure-class RIUs
      - Glass-box reasoning
      - Decision traceability
    industries:
      - Logistics
      - Infrastructure
      - AI platforms
      - Fintech

  - problem_type: Operationalization_and_Scaling
    description: >
      Turning a successful pilot into something that runs every day,
      across customers, teams, and regions.
    common_signals:
      - One-off success
      - Manual steps everywhere
      - Hero-driven operations
    typical_artifacts:
      - SOPs
      - Automation pipelines
      - Training materials
    palette_solution:
      - Restartable execution logs
      - Repeatable RIU chains
      - Maturity promotion rules
    industries:
      - Enterprise SaaS
      - Marketplaces
      - Operations-heavy businesses

  - problem_type: Trust_Governance_and_Adoption
    description: >
      Ensuring humans trust, adopt, and correctly use systems that
      meaningfully affect their work.
    common_signals:
      - Shadow processes
      - Resistance to automation
      - Compliance concerns
    typical_artifacts:
      - Audit trails
      - Explainability docs
      - Governance frameworks
    palette_solution:
      - Transparency-first design
      - Human-in-the-loop enforcement
      - Immutable decision logs
    industries:
      - Finance
      - Healthcare
      - Government
      - Enterprise operations
